The '''Museum of the Holocaust''' in [[Guatemala city]] will be the first [[museum of the Holocaust]] in [[Central America]].<ref>http://www.museodelholocausto.org.gt/en/</ref>
The museum will open in 2016. It currently has a temporary exhibition about the Holocaust by bullets perpetrated by the [[Einsatzgruppen]]. The exhibition is presented by the organization [[Yahad-In Unum|Yahad -In Unum]].<ref>http://www.radiosefarad.com/yahad-in-unum-ante-la-shoa-por-balas-con-marco-gonzalez/</ref>
==Mission== The museum is aiming to educate new generations about the genocide perpetrated against the [[Jews]], the mass executions and persecutions against the [[Romani people|Roma]] as well as other victims of the [[Second World War]].
